SQL_STMT_U.val: select T0.DocNum as 'GRPO Number', T0.CardName as 'Supplier Name', T0.DocDate as 'GRPO Date', T0.U_IDU_Kode_PT as 'Consignee', T0.AuthCode as 'BL Number', T2.DocNum as 'LC Number', T4.CardName as 'Broker Name ', T2.DocDate as 'LC Date', T2.CostSum as 'Cost LC', T4.DocNum as 'Invoice Number', T4.DocDate as 'Invoice Date', T4.DocTotal as 'Total Invoice LC', T5.DocNum as 'Payment Number', T5.DocDate as 'payment Date', T5.DocTotal as 'Total Payment LC' from OPDN T0 join TX_DOCREF TX on T0.ObjType=Tx.BaseType and T0.DocEntry=Tx.BaseEntry inner JOIN ATM.DBO.SYS_GCM S1 ON S1.CONDITION = 'OBJTYPE' AND s1.GCM_ID = T0.ObjType and s1.GCM_ID= ':1' left join OIPF T2 on Tx.DocEntry=t2.DocEntry and Tx.DocType=T2.ObjType --join IPF2 T3 on T2.Docentry=T3.DocEntry join TX_DOCREF TY on T2.ObjType=TY.BaseType and T2.DocEntry=TY.BaseEntry left join OPCH T4 on TY.DocEntry=T4.DocEntry and TY.DocType=T4.ObjType and T4.Canceled='N' join TX_DOCREF TZ on T4.ObjType=TZ.BaseType and T4.DocEntry=TZ.BaseEntry left Join OVPM T5 on TZ.DocEntry=T5.DocEntry and TZ.DocType=T5.ObjType and T5.Canceled='N' where (:2 between ':3' and ':4') AND (T0.DocNum = :5 or :5 = '0') AND (T0.AuthCode = ':6' or ':6'='') order by T2.docnum asc

select T0.DocNum as 'GRPO Number', T0.CardName as 'Supplier Name', T0.DocDate as 'GRPO Date', T0.U_IDU_Kode_PT as 'Consignee', T0.AuthCode as 'BL Number', T2.DocNum as 'LC Number', T4.CardName as 'Broker Name ', T2.DocDate as 'LC Date', T2.CostSum as 'Cost LC', T4.DocNum as 'Invoice Number', T4.DocDate as 'Invoice Date', T4.DocTotal as 'Total Invoice LC', T5.DocNum as 'Payment Number', T5.DocDate as 'payment Date', T5.DocTotal as 'Total Payment LC' from OPDN T0 join TX_DOCREF TX on T0.ObjType=Tx.BaseType and T0.DocEntry=Tx.BaseEntry and T0.DocDate between ':2' and ':3' inner JOIN ATM.DBO.SYS_GCM S1 ON S1.CONDITION = 'OBJTYPE' AND s1.GCM_ID = T0.ObjType and s1.GCM_ID= ':1' left join OIPF T2 on Tx.DocEntry=t2.DocEntry and Tx.DocType=T2.ObjType and T2.docdate between ':2' and ':3' --join IPF2 T3 on T2.Docentry=T3.DocEntry join TX_DOCREF TY on T2.ObjType=TY.BaseType and T2.DocEntry=TY.BaseEntry left join OPCH T4 on TY.DocEntry=T4.DocEntry and TY.DocType=T4.ObjType and T4.Canceled='N'and T4.docdate between ':2' and ':3' join TX_DOCREF TZ on T4.ObjType=TZ.BaseType and T4.DocEntry=TZ.BaseEntry left Join OVPM T5 on TZ.DocEntry=T5.DocEntry and TZ.DocType=T5.ObjType and T5.Canceled='N'and T5.docdate between ':2' and ':3' where (T0.DocNum = :4 or :4= '0') AND (T0.AuthCode = ':5' or ':5'='') order by T2.docnum asc

select * from ( select T0.DocDate as 'Date', T0.DocNum as 'Document Number', T0.CardName as 'Supplier / Vendor', Case when T1.ObjType = 46 then 'Outgoing Payment' end 'Transaction', T1.baseabs as 'DocNum Reference', case when T1.InvType = 204 then 'AP DP' when T1.InvType = 18 then 'AP Invoice' when T1.InvType = 19 then 'AP CN' end 'Transaction Reference', concat ( case when T0.CashAcct = '' then '-' else t0.CashAcct end, '/', case when T0.TrsfrAcct = '' then '-' else t0.trsfracct end, '/', case when T0.CheckAcct = '' then '-' else t0.CheckAcct end ) as 'Cash / Transfer / Check Account', concat ( case when T3.acctName = '' or T3.AcctName is null then '-' else T3.acctName end, '/', case when T2.acctName = '' or T2.AcctName is null then '-' else T2.acctName end, '/', case when T4.acctName = '' or T4.AcctName is null then '-' else T4.acctName end ) as 'Cash / Transfer / Check Name', T1.PaidSum 'Payment Amount', T0.DocCurr as 'Currency', T0.CashSum * T0.DocRate as 'Cash Amount', case when T0.DocCurr <> 'IDR' then T0.CashSum else 0 end as 'Cash Amount FC', T0.TrsfrSum * T0.DocRate as 'Bank Amount', case when T0.DocCurr <> 'IDR' then T0.TrsfrSum else 0 end as 'Bank Amount FC', T0.BcgSum * -1 as 'Bank Charges', T0.Comments as 'Remarks' from OVPM T0 inner join VPM2 T1 on T0.DocEntry = T1.DocNum left join OACT T2 on T0.TrsfrAcct = T2.AcctCode left join OACT T3 on T0.CashAcct = T3.AcctCode left join OACT T4 on T0.CheckAcct = T4.AcctCode where T0.Canceled = 'N' union All select T0.DocDate as 'Date', T0.DocNum as 'Document Number', T0.CardName as 'Supplier / Vendor', Case when T1.ObjType = 46 then 'Outgoing Payment' end 'Transaction', '-' as 'DocNum Reference', 'Type Account' as 'Transaction Reference', concat ( case when T0.CashAcct = '' then '-' else t0.CashAcct end, '/', case when T0.TrsfrAcct = '' then '-' else t0.trsfracct end, '/', case when T0.CheckAcct = '' then '-' else t0.CheckAcct end ) as 'Cash / Transfer / Check Account', concat ( case when T3.acctName = '' or T3.AcctName is null then '-' else T3.acctName end, '/', case when T2.acctName = '' or T2.AcctName is null then '-' else T2.acctName end, '/', case when T4.acctName = '' or T4.AcctName is null then '-' else T4.acctName end ) as 'Cash / Transfer / Check Name', T1.SumApplied 'Payment Amount', T0.DocCurr as 'Currency', T0.CashSum * T0.DocRate as 'Cash Amount', case when T0.DocCurr <> 'IDR' then T0.CashSum else 0 end as 'Cash Amount FC', T0.TrsfrSum * T0.DocRate as 'Bank Amount', case when T0.DocCurr <> 'IDR' then T0.TrsfrSum else 0 end as 'Bank Amount FC', T0.BcgSum * -1 as 'Bank Charges', T0.Comments as 'Remarks' from OVPM T0 inner join VPM4 T1 on T0.DocEntry = T1.DocNum left join OACT T2 on T0.TrsfrAcct = T2.AcctCode left join OACT T3 on T0.CashAcct = T3.AcctCode left join OACT T4 on T0.CheckAcct = T4.AcctCode where T0.Canceled = 'N' union All select T0.DocDate as 'Date', T0.DocNum as 'Document Number', T0.CardName as 'Supplier / Vendor', Case when T1.ObjType = 24 then 'Incoming Payment' end 'Transaction', T1.baseabs as 'DocNum Reference', case when T1.InvType = 203 then 'AR DP' when T1.InvType = 13 then 'AR Invoice' when T1.InvType = 14 then 'AR CN' end 'Transaction Reference', concat ( case when T0.CashAcct = '' then '-' else t0.CashAcct end, '/', case when T0.TrsfrAcct = '' then '-' else t0.trsfracct end, '/', case when T0.CheckAcct = '' then '-' else t0.CheckAcct end ) as 'Cash / Transfer / Check Account', concat ( case when T3.acctName = '' or T3.AcctName is null then '-' else T3.acctName end, '/', case when T2.acctName = '' or T2.AcctName is null then '-' else T2.acctName end, '/', case when T4.acctName = '' or T4.AcctName is null then '-' else T4.acctName end ) as 'Cash / Transfer / Check Name', T1.PaidSum 'Payment Amount', T0.DocCurr as 'Currency', T0.CashSum * T0.DocRate as 'Cash Amount', case when T0.DocCurr <> 'IDR' then T0.CashSum else 0 end as 'Cash Amount FC', T0.TrsfrSum * T0.DocRate as 'Bank Amount', case when T0.DocCurr <> 'IDR' then T0.TrsfrSum else 0 end as 'Bank Amount FC', T0.BcgSum * -1 as 'Bank Charges', T0.Comments as 'Remarks' from ORCT T0 inner join RCT2 T1 on T0.DocEntry = T1.DocNum left join OACT T2 on T0.TrsfrAcct = T2.AcctCode left join OACT T3 on T0.CashAcct = T3.AcctCode left join OACT T4 on T0.CheckAcct = T4.AcctCode where T0.Canceled = 'N' Union All select T0.DocDate as 'Date', T0.DocNum as 'Document Number', T0.CardName as 'Supplier / Vendor', Case when T1.ObjType = 24 then 'Incoming Payment' end 'Transaction', '-' as 'DocNum Reference', 'Type Account' as 'Transaction Reference', concat ( case when T0.CashAcct = '' then '-' else t0.CashAcct end, '/', case when T0.TrsfrAcct = '' then '-' else t0.trsfracct end, '/', case when T0.CheckAcct = '' then '-' else t0.CheckAcct end ) as 'Cash / Transfer / Check Account', concat ( case when T3.acctName = '' or T3.AcctName is null then '-' else T3.acctName end, '/', case when T2.acctName = '' or T2.AcctName is null then '-' else T2.acctName end, '/', case when T4.acctName = '' or T4.AcctName is null then '-' else T4.acctName end ) as 'Cash / Transfer / Check Name', T1.SumApplied 'Payment Amount', T0.DocCurr as 'Currency', T0.CashSum * T0.DocRate as 'Cash Amount', case when T0.DocCurr <> 'IDR' then T0.CashSum else 0 end as 'Cash Amount FC', T0.TrsfrSum * T0.DocRate as 'Bank Amount', case when T0.DocCurr <> 'IDR' then T0.TrsfrSum else 0 end as 'Bank Amount FC', T0.BcgSum * -1 as 'Bank Charges', T0.Comments as 'Remarks' from ORCT T0 inner join RCT4 T1 on T0.DocEntry = T1.DocNum left join OACT T2 on T0.TrsfrAcct = T2.AcctCode left join OACT T3 on T0.CashAcct = T3.AcctCode left join OACT T4 on T0.CheckAcct = T4.AcctCode where T0.Canceled = 'N' ) as X where x.Date between ':1' and ':2' Order by X.[Transaction], x.Date asc
